    <item>
      <title>韩国对华直接投资流量创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/south-korea-direct-investment-flow-to-china-falls-most-on-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年，韩国对中国的直接投资流量降幅创三十多年前的最高纪录，这表明随着美国努力减少其盟友对北京的依赖，两国之间的经济关系正在减弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/south-korea-direct-investment-flow-to-china-falls-most-on-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 02:12:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本 GPIF 将在中断四年后恢复外国股票借贷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/japan-gpif-to-resume-lending-foreign-stocks-after-4-year-hiatus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大的日本国家养老基金将恢复借出外国股票，此举将为卖空者提供更多股票，该基金四年前暂停了这种做法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/japan-gpif-to-resume-lending-foreign-stocks-after-4-year-hiatus</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 01:39:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
